OL,3,C'We will fight for our members' -
OL,4,Csteelworkers' union to ballot for
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FMembers of the Community union will be
OL,8,Fballoted for industrial action over
OL,9,FTata Steel's plans to close both blast
OL,10,Ffurnaces at its site, which .
OL,12,FFollowing a meeting of union reps in
OL,13,FPort Talbot on Tuesday 26 March,
OL,14,FCommunity, the union which represents
OL,15,Fmore steelworkers than any other
OL,16,Funion, has agreed details for a ballot
OL,17,Fon industrial action.
