OL,3,C'We will fight for our members' -
OL,4,Csteelworkers' union to ballot for
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,FThe union will this week be serving
OL,8,Fnotice to Tata on its intention to
OL,9,Fballot for industrial action, with the
OL,10,Fballot then commencing in two weeks'
OL,11,Ftime.
OL,13,FAlun Davies, National Officer for
OL,14,FSteel at Community Union, said: "We've
OL,15,Fbeen clear from the beginning that all
OL,16,Fcards were on the table to protect our
OL,17,Fmembers jobs and save our steel
OL,18,Findustry.
