OL,3,C'We will fight for our members' -
OL,4,Csteelworkers' union to ballot for
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"It has become evident over the recent
OL,8,Fdays that Tata are not serious about
OL,9,Fengaging with our Multi-Union plan for
OL,10,Fsteel, which they themselves have
OL,11,Fadmitted is viable and could be the
OL,12,Froad towards a profitable future for
OL,13,Ftheir UK steel sites.
OL,15,F"Therefore, we've been given little
OL,16,Fchoice other than to put this issue to
OL,17,Four members and ask them if they want
OL,18,Fto take the next step towards
OL,19,Findustrial action.
