OL,3,C'We will fight for our members' -
OL,4,Csteelworkers' union to ballot for
OL,5,Cstrike
OL,7,F"Now let me be crystal clear on this.
OL,8,FCommunity and our members haven't
OL,9,Fchosen this fight. We've put forward a
OL,10,Fcredible and workable alternative to
OL,11,FTata, but it's through their lack of
OL,12,Faction, and their unwillingness to
OL,13,Fsteer away from their damaging plan
OL,14,Fthat we've come to this point.
OL,16,F"We will fight for our members, their
OL,17,Fjobs, and their communities."
